00:38:09,700 --> 00:38:17,940
where the spike in the unemployment rate is something like 10 times the largest unemployment spike in the last 50 years.

526
00:38:17,940 --> 00:38:19,660
So that's a big thing.

527
00:38:19,660 --> 00:38:23,280
I have had to give up my business for the time being.

528
00:38:23,280 --> 00:38:25,760
I mean, it will come back and all will be well.

