00:38:53,980 --> 00:38:58,200
But people should be worried about all of the people who have no income and no savings, of whom they're a great thing.

537
00:38:58,420 --> 00:38:59,960
Yeah, and that's why I say I'm privileged.

538
00:38:59,960 --> 00:39:04,300
I think I am still employed and my job does not require me to go anywhere.

539
00:39:04,300 --> 00:39:07,740
So I think I am incredibly lucky that that is the case.

