00:39:18,200 --> 00:39:23,980
But I did order something at 12 p.m. on Friday that was delivered at 12 p.m. on Saturday last weekend,

546
00:39:23,980 --> 00:39:26,800
which I was a little bit confused by because I thought the post was taking longer.

547
00:39:26,920 --> 00:39:28,760
And that one just seemed to sail through.

