00:40:34,860 --> 00:40:36,580
But that also arrived.

569
00:40:36,580 --> 00:40:43,980
And we have been getting takeaway more than usual in a sort of effort to support our local restaurants.

570
00:40:43,980 --> 00:40:46,120
And that has been, again, very efficient.

